{"thig5.4:0.1":"Therigatha 5.4 ","thig5.4:0.2":"Pancakanipata ","thig5.4:0.3":"Sundarinandatherigatha ","thig5.4:1.1":"“Aturam asucim putim, ","thig5.4:1.2":"passa nande samussayam; ","thig5.4:1.3":"Asubhaya cittam bhavehi, ","thig5.4:1.4":"ekaggam susamahitam. ","thig5.4:2.1":"Yatha idam tatha etam, ","thig5.4:2.2":"yatha etam tatha idam; ","thig5.4:2.3":"Duggandham putikam vati, ","thig5.4:2.4":"balanam abhinanditam. ","thig5.4:3.1":"Evametam avekkhanti, ","thig5.4:3.2":"rattindivamatandita; ","thig5.4:3.3":"Tato sakaya pannaya, ","thig5.4:3.4":"abhinibbijjha dakkhisam”. ","thig5.4:4.1":"“Tassa me appamattaya, ","thig5.4:4.2":"vicinantiya yoniso; ","thig5.4:4.3":"Yathabhutam ayam kayo, ","thig5.4:4.4":"dittho santarabahiro. ","thig5.4:5.1":"Atha nibbindaham kaye, ","thig5.4:5.2":"ajjhattanca virajjaham; ","thig5.4:5.3":"Appamatta visamyutta, ","thig5.4:5.4":"upasantamhi nibbuta”ti. ","thig5.4:6.1":"… Sundarinanda theri …. "}